    • onSaveButtonClick

      protected void onSaveButtonClick(javafx.event.ActionEvent e)
      Event handler/listener that fires from the save button, saves the input data as a new part object in inventory and redirects back to the main IMSApplication screen. Checks and throws exceptions for incorrect input types and displays a popup error for incorrect inventory ranges and incorrect min/max values.
